remium-discount mechanism between perpetual and index prices, with rates applied at the top of each hour. The platform uses a 0.01% funding rate cap per interval, with actual rates determined by the 1-hour TWAP of the premium/discount. Given the hourly frequency versus traditional 8-hour cycles, funding payments are smaller but more frequent, requiring active position management."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
